ed fallback test has been removed/reverted, leaving only the supported `PureJavaReflectionProvider` coverage that already passed and covered the five reachable call sites.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_045a421a425e7438016a25847cd7348196a62e28f7be710ede\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1512, \"output\": 764, \"cacheRead\": 83456, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 85732, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1780843632432, \"responseId\": \"resp_045a421a425e7438016a25847122e08196a7e2ac77c3f931bc\"}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.thoughtworks.xstream:xstream:1.4.20/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T14-36-02-921114Z.log:7274:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_045a421a425e7438016a258471ff448196a2d7a866678e22bc\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"content\\\":[],\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABqJYR88GiuXX6vmL9dlfV1B-AVoHJMPR4164QAgaBgysC1U2ta1JiMoIWH_s3dcmSfMqnmZ7DD3SzOULNYsGk0ddME2Wq_X1ZgYe8IBYNvsgasyW4UNjIZTvWTc2-705YdIbqZjoEMVTzhsK7t-SipqoGP6xla312gBQbCdEAXQNfsSwyOMtNPsDHl0YKx7C0eT0eeOVi0nXtkZ7yOwaERwMP0uIQbe07rSGRjU_Xa-DMgL7YdyC4I4WEvdF8j4ohjhWdlXy99gGYmIrcdSK3LDJhmb48AdGFtZl7OZHqtN_FLtecZrLKV2aAlrJ0lhcuaqxyj7Wb20LaBkVxqWGvAob__7cqkNyS4kByMXFohAJGGpCQl2Im8kluFNeVgZVRXfZ9NetfLTj1LeUqLMTuaDX5XyDvj9s9SH58jnKwa1-raEBCVKdJ0kK-BjAyTN1geTm6figM11ta4b-pPSH-dvScjAe5srERRh9NjXnuPPi2lePpvsj4fwxm2ovI4E3C7v5QT_Qnpr-rJDe4to79foOi5VMP1RRax0JoSIsJ058JpiwGpQgXWCKySXlTXnHcIU1ghNzfVOUpRNt3tjIIY0S4A6d3k-bHJVYtvbDl2XB6qBCz9YhU7HbS4SG17O2dq6-eYH4cJB-fOc_LBv0xYwTjh7cUtBuf5yxCPRrALaeY_x97gzrYB672kigpS7fKXdyOXl2wL4BbjaFtahC--X3zVzvo1Q0Rx4kdSCJ6xHpK4OcxXpn9UtU3yp8t7lvhHIgolRW8vYrkKsNwH25ZvMGDYCSbB9_c